  "title": "Blood N Particles Mod",
  "description": "Adds blood and damage particles to players and mobs for a more immersive experience",
  "body": "![What is this mod?](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/76a49f5fea336835463107550948f29444aba36a.png)\n\nThis is a MOD that consists of adding a touch of immersion to the game, adding blood, particles and sounds every time you take damage and grant damage to your enemies!\n  \n<p align=\"center\"><strong>All Overworld, Nether and End Mobs can bleed!</strong></p>\n\n<iframe width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/pi-fuXMWtxQ\" title=\"YouTube video player\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen></iframe>  \n\n<p><strong> </strong></p>\n\n<div align=\"center\">\n  <img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/1187/400/snapshot_triple-png.png\" width=\"640\" height=\"320\"/>\n</div>\n\n\n<p><strong> </strong></p>\n\n<div align=\"center\">\n  <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/3f9d406bdc108043521be21babeae92796f9b52e.png\" width=\"200\" height=\"67\" alt=\"Available for NeoForge\" />\n  <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/f45550c75cf3467bb11a2c9adec01c4b20231d08.png\" width=\"200\" height=\"67\" alt=\"Available for Fabric\" />\n  <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/0bb4fb3681e8cc1f3c3a6053475c4295e5b55ed2.png\" width=\"200\" height=\"67\" alt=\"Available for Forge\" />\n</div>\n<p><strong> </strong></p>\n\n*If you have any suggestions for the Mod or want to report a bug, don't forget to leave it in the comments :D*\n\n\n![Support](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/3438885f7a6c933e17c5e634a7aefdc4f48da308.png)\n\nIf you like to support us, you can Join our  <span style=\"color: #3598db;\"><a style=\"color: #3598db;\" href=\"https://discord.gg/N6TsrGvzvZ\" rel=\"nofollow\">Discord</a></span> or Support us monetarily on our <span style=\"color: #3598db;\">&nbsp;<a style=\"color: #3598db;\" href=\"https://www.patreon.com/RenovatedStudios\" rel=\"nofollow\">Patreon</a></span>\n\n<span style=\"color: #3598db;\"><a href=\"https://discord.gg/N6TsrGvzvZ\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1017834/description_f9406618-0e4f-4d0a-92da-5376ba49b9e8.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"354\" height=\"82\"></a><a href=\"https://www.patreon.com/RenovatedStudios\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1017834/description_fb2b698d-66ca-4888-a0c3-460d706e5304.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"354\" height=\"82\"></a></span>",
